title: Jonathan Chávez
text: Jonathan Daniel Chávez (born 8 January 1989, in <a href="La%20Plata">La Plata</a>) is an <a href="Argentina">Argentine</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> who plays for <a href="Deportes%20Vallenar">Deportes Vallenar</a>.
